00:13:14.240 --> 00:13:16.280
that also have to be worked out.

00:13:16.760 --> 00:13:21.320
It's not all just about user experience and things like that.

00:13:22.459 --> 00:13:22.980
Sure.

00:13:23.740 --> 00:13:24.420
That makes sense.

