01:10:26.960 --> 01:10:29.680
But yeah, it's going to be interesting to see where it goes.

01:10:29.860 --> 01:10:31.400
It's a challenge.

01:10:31.680 --> 01:10:35.480
But I really like your ideas that we're going to rise to it.

01:10:35.560 --> 01:10:39.880
We've solved the hard enough problems now that this new thing is a problem.

